summary:
I am a creative, analytical, and results-driven person. These three characteristics, along with a lifelong desire to build a more equitable and sustainable world have driven my educational pursuits as well as my work experience. I am excited to be part of a team that thinks on a large scale about solving systemic issues and works with the nitty-gritty details of actually getting the job done. 

As a founding member of a young non-profit that is exactly what I get to do. We think large scale about food systems and hunger in Philadelphia- but we are also on the ground working with the community to make sure our neighbors are getting the food they need today.
